      Unchecked          2.d.2- NullPointerException
      Unchecked          2.d.3- NumberFormatException
      Unchecked          2.d.4- IndexOutOfBoundsException (ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException , StringIndexOutOfBoundsException )
